NEXUS Patent Grant and Reservation Notice
==========================================

Effective Date: April 3, 2026
Author: said885 <frensh5@proton.me>

SCOPE
=====

This notice applies to the following original works contained in the
NEXUS project repository:

1. The NEXUS Hybrid KEM construction combining Kyber1024 (NIST FIPS 203)
   with X25519 key exchange via HKDF-SHA3-512 key derivation.

2. The NEXUS Post-Quantum Double Ratchet extension integrating KEM-based
   ratcheting with classical Diffie-Hellman ratcheting.

3. The NEXUS Zero-Knowledge Relay architecture for metadata-private
   message routing without server-side content or relationship knowledge.

4. The NEXUS Sealed Sender protocol for anonymous message submission
   with post-quantum authentication.

5. The NEXUS Envelope Encryption scheme for multi-layer message protection
   with forward secrecy guarantees.

6. All formal verification models (TLA+ specifications) for the X3DH
   and Double Ratchet protocols as implemented in NEXUS.

